headline: Tracking the Narrative for PepsiCo as Strategic Shifts Reshape Its Growth Story
summary: The consensus analyst price target for PepsiCo has recently seen only a marginal shift, moving from $154.24 to $152.57. This subtle adjustment reflects a combination of bullish optimism over new energy drink initiatives and caution regarding international sales trends.
